Navigate to OpenSearch Dashboards, choose Dev Tools, and index a sample document:
PUT accounts/_doc/0
{ "ssn": "123", "id-": "456"
}

To test a read event, send the following request:
GET accounts/_search
{ "query": { "match_all": {} }
}

